      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 and that designation is fully earned. From bumper to bumper, this car presents as flawless: the exterior paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with no scratches, chips, or blemishes to speak of. The interior is equally immaculate, with pristine upholstery, spotless trim, and all controls and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs with smooth, confident power, and all mechanical systems are in excellent working order with no known issues. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for \u2014 it drives as good as it looks, and it looks outstanding. Ideal for a discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
